<paragraph pageId="196" pageNumber="197">
(Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 175" captionStartId="F175" captionText="Figure 175. Distribution of Conostegia oligocephala." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.67.6703.figure175" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/96533" pageId="196" pageNumber="197">175</figureCitation>
